Subject: [PATCH] ASoC/soundwire: intel: pass hdac_bus pointer for link management
Mime-version: 1.0
Content-type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-transfer-encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 881cf1e9df731e6dc238ca83067c17c782e2a059
